{"title":"Found: Aventon Level Commuter e-Bike is feature packed, surprisingly affordable","link":"https://bikerumor.com/found-aventon-level-commuter-e-bike-is-feature-packed-surprisingly-affordable/","date":1637680943000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110311/aventon-level-commuter-ebike-feature-story.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"596\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110311/aventon-level-commuter-ebike-feature-story-800x596.jpg\" alt=\"aventon level commuter e-bike\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110311/aventon-level-commuter-ebike-feature-story-800x596.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110311/aventon-level-commuter-ebike-feature-story-297x221.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110311/aventon-level-commuter-ebike-feature-story-120x89.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110311/aventon-level-commuter-ebike-feature-story-768x573.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110311/aventon-level-commuter-ebike-feature-story.jpg 1501w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-272824\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>If you want a basic-yet-capable commuter e-bike that comes standard with everything you need to get to and from work, school, or the store, the <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=a41b063c-52a4-4d87-8f09-d6c71998ed15&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Faventon-level-commuter-ebike&amp;ctc=brspoutdoorbikingaventonlevel|xid:fr1637682287825fdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-orig-url=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=a41b063c-52a4-4d87-8f09-d6c71998ed15&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Faventon-level-commuter-ebike&amp;ctc=brspoutdoorbikingaventonlevel\" data-ml-id=\"0\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1637682287825fdf\">Aventon Level</a> is worth a look.</p><p>Featuring full coverage fenders, a heavy-duty rear rack, and a powerful motor, the Level can assist up to 28mph while you’re pedaling, or cruise along at 20mph without pedaling by using the throttle. Add in a big battery, fast charging, and average 40-mile range, and it should be all the bike you need for daily rides. Here’s a closer look at all the details…</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110307/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110307/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-5.jpg\" alt=\"aventon level commuter e-bike shown from the side\" width=\"1600\" height=\"973\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110307/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-5.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110307/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-5-297x181.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110307/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-5-800x487.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110307/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-5-120x73.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110307/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-5-768x467.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110307/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-5-1536x934.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>The <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=a41b063c-52a4-4d87-8f09-d6c71998ed15&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Faventon-level-commuter-ebike&amp;ctc=brspoutdoorbikingaventonlevel|xid:fr1637682287825fei\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-orig-url=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=a41b063c-52a4-4d87-8f09-d6c71998ed15&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Faventon-level-commuter-ebike&amp;ctc=brspoutdoorbikingaventonlevel\" data-ml-id=\"1\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1637682287825fei\">Aventon Level</a> is their flagship commuter e-bike, getting streamlined looks thanks to an integrated battery and smoothly shaped tubes. It comes in three sizes to fit riders from 5’1″ up to 6’4″, and in both standard and step-thru models.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110302/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110302/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-3.jpg\" alt=\"aventon level commuter e-bike with hidden battery and rear hub motor\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110302/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-3.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110302/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-3-297x297.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110302/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-3-800x800.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110302/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-3-120x120.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110302/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-3-768x768.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110302/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-3-125x125.jpg 125w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Unlike a lot of electric-assist bikes in this price range, the hidden Li-Ion battery inside a downtube compartment delivers upscale aesthetics. It’s removable for easier charging (but you can also charge it on the bike) and packs 672Wh.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110305/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110305/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-4.jpg\" alt=\"aventon level commuter e-bike with hidden battery and rear hub motor\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110305/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-4.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110305/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-4-297x297.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110305/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-4-800x800.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110305/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-4-120x120.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110305/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-4-768x768.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110305/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-4-125x125.jpg 125w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Combine that with the 500W (750W peak) brushless rear hub motor and it’ll deliver an average of 40 miles of range per charge, and assist at up to 28mph. An 8-speed drivetrain helps you keep it in the right gear and cadence, too.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110300/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110300/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-2.jpg\" alt=\"closeup of controls and display on aventon level commuter e-bike\" width=\"1625\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110300/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-2.jpg 1625w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110300/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-2-297x146.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110300/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-2-800x394.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110300/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-2-120x59.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110300/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-2-768x378.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110300/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-2-1536x756.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1625px) 100vw, 1625px\"></a></p><p>The Level comes with a remote switch so you can adjust the amount of assist it provides. There’s also a throttle for those times when you don’t feel like pedaling, or just need a little kickstart to get rolling from a stop (like when starting on a hill).</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110257/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110257/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-1.jpg\" alt=\"front angle view of aventon level commuter e-bike\" width=\"1400\" height=\"1058\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110257/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-1.jpg 1400w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110257/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-1-297x224.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110257/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-1-800x605.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110257/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-1-120x91.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/27110257/Aventon-Level-affordable-commuter-ebike-details-1-768x580.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\"></a></p><p>Features like a sturdy rear rack that’s attached directly to the frame, and full coverage fenders, add a lot of utility to the bike. Add pannier bags or a child seat or rear basket to haul gear for work or school, or get your wee ones out for some fresh air.</p><p>The bikes come with wide all-conditions tires on 27.5″ rims for better roll over performance, plus a 75mm travel front suspension fork to tame the bumps. (Note: Fork shown is different from what’s shipping <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=ale&amp;pw=147535&amp;mi=19453&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fblogs%2Faventon_bikes%2Febike-components-update&amp;ctc=xid:fr1637682287825bbg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"ugc\" data-orig-url=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=ale&amp;pw=147535&amp;mi=19453&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fblogs%2Faventon_bikes%2Febike-components-update\" data-ml-id=\"2\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1637682287825bbg\">due to supply chain issues</a>…all bikes are currently delivered with a Zoom brand fork)</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/08162214/aventon-level-step-thru-commuter-ebike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/08162214/aventon-level-step-thru-commuter-ebike.jpg\" alt=\"aventon level commuter e-bike with step through frame and hidden battery\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1418\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/08162214/aventon-level-step-thru-commuter-ebike.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/08162214/aventon-level-step-thru-commuter-ebike-297x263.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/08162214/aventon-level-step-thru-commuter-ebike-800x709.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/08162214/aventon-level-step-thru-commuter-ebike-120x106.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/08162214/aventon-level-step-thru-commuter-ebike-768x681.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/08162214/aventon-level-step-thru-commuter-ebike-1536x1361.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>The <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=a41b063c-52a4-4d87-8f09-d6c71998ed15&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Faventon-level-commuter-ebike&amp;ctc=brspoutdoorbikingaventonlevel|xid:fr1637682287825ihj\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-orig-url=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=a41b063c-52a4-4d87-8f09-d6c71998ed15&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Faventon-level-commuter-ebike&amp;ctc=brspoutdoorbikingaventonlevel\" data-ml-id=\"3\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1637682287825ihj\">Level Step-Through Commuter bike</a> comes with all the same features, but in two sizes -S/M and M/L- to fit riders from 4’11” to 6’2″. Retail price for both models is $1,799, and are in stock now as of this story going live. All bikes are delivered mostly assembled with only the front wheel and (fully equipped) handlebar needing to be installed.</p><p>All Aventon bikes come with a 14 day return policy and one year warranty.</p><p><em>This post is sponsored by Aventon. Learn more about the <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=a41b063c-52a4-4d87-8f09-d6c71998ed15&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Faventon-level-commuter-ebike&amp;ctc=brspoutdoorbikingaventonlevel|xid:fr1637682287825jba\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-orig-url=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=a41b063c-52a4-4d87-8f09-d6c71998ed15&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Faventon-level-commuter-ebike&amp;ctc=brspoutdoorbikingaventonlevel\" data-ml-id=\"6\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1637682287825jba\">Standard Level</a> and <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=a41b063c-52a4-4d87-8f09-d6c71998ed15&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Faventon-level-commuter-ebike&amp;ctc=brspoutdoorbikingaventonlevel|xid:fr1637682287825dha\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-orig-url=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=a41b063c-52a4-4d87-8f09-d6c71998ed15&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aventon.com%2Fproducts%2Faventon-level-commuter-ebike&amp;ctc=brspoutdoorbikingaventonlevel\" data-ml-id=\"7\" data-ml=\"true\" data-xid=\"fr1637682287825dha\">Step-Thru Level</a> eBikes at Aventon.com.</em></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"b1fe88278481910db45fb78032a4ad11cb1e843be80a5ebb2a5dc6e70009e49b","category":"Cycling"}